  <summary date="2015-09-18T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Perpetual POW/MIA Stamp Act

Directs the Postmaster General to provide for the issuance of a forever stamp that honors the sacrifices of the members of the U.S. Armed Forces who have been prisoners, missing, or unaccounted for and that depicts the National League of Families POW/MIA flag.</summary>
